reviewText: Especially liked the Shay locomotives, the scenery and a great history lesson as well

My husband and I could sit and watch Trains and railroads all day long. This is a must. I am so glad I have Amazon Prime. Just sit back and enjoy the scenery on this there are different locations on this video YOU WILL LOVE. A MUST WATCH... More like this AMAZON!
Excellent picture quality, beautiful scenic views and interesting historical information. This DVD is a must for the railroad enthusiast.
My husband's family grew up in West Virginia and this was a very neat show to watch.  It almost felt like being there.  The Cass Scenic Railroad is truly one of America's treasures.
Well done ! Full of historiclal facts,and beautiful scenic shots, especialy drone views.
Watching rail way videos are always good, Brings back memories.

I have been a fan of Delay in Block productions on You Tube for more than a year know. The prodection values are very high, and the films are informative and fun to watch. This dvd is no exception to the rule. I'm very happy to have purchased it. No film about a railroad subject can cover everything, but I am very pleased with this effort on the part of Delay in Block.
